    public class LogManagerWindow
extends javax.swing.JFrame
    Store, update, and manage the set of LogItems that make up a ScriptManager session log with GUI management of log properties and features.
    Author:
    Olivia Lang
    See Also:
    ScriptManagerGUI, Serialized Form
